column3: “Found this in NJ and knocked me out. Killed the tremors, the pain, and brought back my appetite with a vengeance. Dry eyes and a headband/goggle effect is a price worth paying, though over-indulgence may lead to some slight spin/vertigo sensation. Made me a little jumpy at first through a bong but settled into a smooth and relaxed high which also killed the leg spasms. Vaped through a volcano at 210 degrees C twice w...”

“Got ahold of this strain from a good friend. He picked it up from some place in Anaheim. We rolled it in a joint and it packed a mean punch! the nugs were frosty and solid with a great smell! I'd love to try it again.”
“good strain. great energizing kush but enough will get u tired.great for daytime and night use, it's sweet and smooth like most kush. I prefer more of the indica kush tho or OG”
“Good head high, definitely a relaxing buzz. Good laughs, serious munchies, good for insomnia or stress.”
“the best of both worlds, very resigning, uplifting, sweet smelling and amazing for pain”
“strong scented with uplifting high heavy kick to the smoke and hits you in the top of the head”
“The smell and taste is to die for! Smells sweet, citrusy, and piney. The resin production is unreal. My fingers were very sticky after breaking up a little for a bowl. Awesome stuff!”
“Good weed !”
“Good weed !”
“the best of both worlds, very resigning, uplifting, sweet smelling and amazing for pain”

“its a sativa dominant hybrid (70% sativa/30% indica) strain that is a potent cross between the insanely popular Jack Herer X OG Kush strains. This insanely dank bud boasts a moderately high THC level ranging from 13-22% on average and a myriad of extremely potent sativa and indica effects. Jack OG has an aroma of sweet candy with a hint of pungent skunk and a taste of sweet vanilla candy with a floral skunk aftertast...”
“Good head high, definitely a relaxing buzz. Good laughs, serious munchies, good for insomnia or stress.”

“A rather pleasant high. Now that I've smoked it a few times, I kinda like it's lazy effect - it's not enough to put me down, but it's enough to make me feel nice. Quite strong and very enjoyable, especially at night. If you can get your hands on this definitely try it.”

“This has better pain control with less of the high that he has experienced with all other high CBD flowers he's tried. 

He had a headache at a 5, came down pretty quick to a 3 which is usual.  

Doesn't seem anxious.  
Not goofy like he's high.  
Seems to be concentrating on movie. 

He really likes it.”
“Lovely, large buds with good hairs and great taste. Not to fluffy but not to dense. Just right with no burnout!”
“With a little bit more of medical properties this could be one of my favorites.”
“In love! It puts me in the best mood. It doesn't give me that super foggy head high so I can still completely function. It is my go to when I need an attitude adjustment.”
“Yousa, hit it and it came on slowly, then pushed up and through to a higher state of a killer, but inventive buzz. Nosed dived into sleep at the tail end of the adventure. Very buzzy.”

“Very good bud to smoke at the end of a hard day of work. Not very good for work, though.  You definitely feel a little bit lazier than usual. Visual high is amazing, and good for some last minute sketching before sleeping.”
“bomb”
“Taste Great, Dence Buds,”

“Jack Herer X OG Kush

Love OG Jack.. Great golden-green flowers that smell like heaven and taste even better. I found this strain to be great for low budget smokers like myself. If I smoked alittle in the morning with coffee/tea, I got a great daytime boost that kept the pain at bay, but did not couchlock. At night, if I smoked a little bit more.. I'd get relaxed and sleepy, sleeping the whole night. This strain, if ...”
“Pretty happy about what i just got :)”

“Just smoked a 1g 13.97% preroll of OG Jack" but I think I'm in the right place. Hits like a sativa/kush but is quite forgiving - I didn't have to pause the session once. I have a high tolerance for Indicas as I have a fractured skull and c4 vertebrae
column4: I think  that helped smooth out any uncomfortable effects that could.be experienced by this incredible strain. My first time with Jack and I'm in love with the euphori...”"

column3: “This was an alright hybrid (jack herrer x kush), but the high wasnt anything special. after smoking a blunt of this i had to sit down outside on my lawn, and i didnt realize until the end of the blunt i was sitting in a puddle of water as it had just rained. the high is more towards the indica end of the spectrum, yet the couch lock is not unbearable. being a sativa lover this did not appeal to me. jack kush is your ...”
